{"tid":1630953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想識前線手足除左發夢做魔法師，邊度可以識到？","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:13:42.000Z","uid":82725,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1e3b826a320d1ff4bbd9fe49a1c39879a9e11432","tid":1630953,"uid":82725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"先聲明，我六月至今係香城Online不嬲做開遊呻詩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我身邊啲人都藍到發黑，不論公司定屋企人。完全無乜企得前同深黃，我其實想轉全職做勇武，但多數要小組形式先唔會落單比狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想攬炒，但唔想送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪手足多數都係搵返自己啲同學/朋友/伴侶出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe7b5577df05326c22543b0d592b141b925c1bd","tid":1630953,"uid":242358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"師弟here<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申廢柴工兵"},{"pid":"f3ad59cf9bc4dfc9344aced180ac8c95d0a5eb79","tid":1630953,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師<span style=\"color: red;\">兄</span>here<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申廢柴工兵</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d67aa10d8b159233cd742b5aebd2c614e1407658","tid":1630953,"uid":308644,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾狗咬係睇你自己個意識足唔足夠<br />\n問多啲自己邊到有狗幾時要走走邊到<br />\n上嚟連登搵隊友自求多福<br />\n因為無人知你係狗定人地係狗"},{"pid":"3cf2bf22c2dbc36466388d4232806fbb20a7632d","tid":1630953,"uid":82725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d67aa10d8b159233cd742b5aebd2c614e1407658","tid":1630953,"uid":308644,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾狗咬係睇你自己個意識足唔足夠<br />\n問多啲自己邊到有狗幾時要走走邊到<br />\n上嚟連登搵隊友自求多福<br />\n因為無人知你係狗定人地係狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:24:52.000